#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/optimize/seo.rst:369
msgid ""
"Flectra's pictograms are implemented using a font (`Font Awesome "
"<https://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/icons/>`__ in most Flectra themes)."
